{
  "stem": "182.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 326.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "My father fell on the bus, and my brother got very angry and said, don't you push my father!",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And just because of that-- and my father pacified my brother, that leave my son, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Nothing is happening to me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And just because of that, every time we stopped, they came and looked for my brother and threatened that they were going to do something to him.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "So my mother was terribly, terribly worried and upset.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Anyway, we came by the night, and they put the trucks on a ferry and we went across the Dniester River and continued our trip.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "We came all the way to a little town in Poland that's called Jagielnica.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there-- also, they wanted to make everything very dramatic.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They unloaded us by the cemetery.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And next to the cemetery there was quarry.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so there was a big, big hole.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the soldiers-- the gendarmes told us, look that way.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There is the border.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now remember that if you come that way, we shoot you all.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Don't you ever come back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they went away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They drove away, and they left us there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then the Ukrainian-- they really were not policemen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were, I think, just people who lived there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or some were policemen maybe, but they didn't have any uniforms.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had a gun, but they didn't have any uniforms.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They came, and they told us to line up and march.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And while we were going-- and we didn't know where they are taking us-- my father who spoke Ukrainian told them, that, you know, you be careful what you do with us, because the Hungarians are smart.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They want that you should have the blood on your hands.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They want to be clean.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
